Dylan: Brave and courageous young lady, are you okay?

Sharice: YES, SIR!!!

Young Lizard: Aren't we the worst of enemies? Why would they help us?

Fredrica: Plus, with a handsome foreign stud like you...ain't nobody gonna be upset with a hot, steamy exotic fling~

Angelia: Sophie! You're safe!
Sophie: Eh? You're that nice lady from the slums...

Dylan: Fearing another conflict between the two nations, the Queen of the Kingdom of the Sun sent a secret message to Queen Diana.
Sione: It wasn't easy, but Diana eventually agreed to talk in secret. She sent a group of elite soldiers to bring our Queen here.

Sophie: Forgive, I...I...don't quite understand...

Sophie: Why are you all looking at her...wait a second...NO WAY!?
Angelia: ...I'm sorry, I never had a chance to introduce myself. Please, forgive me.
Angelia: I am Angelia Carlos, Queen of the Kingdom of the Sun.
Angelia: ——Nice to meet you, Sophie.
